---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About"
  description="Learn about DevTools - Free online developer tools for everyone."
>
  <article class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1>About DevTools</h1>
    
    <p>
      DevTools is a collection of free, fast, and private developer tools. All tools run entirely 
      in your browser, ensuring your data never leaves your device.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      To provide developers with high-quality, free tools that make their work easier and more efficient. 
      We believe that essential developer tools should be accessible to everyone, without registration 
      or hidden costs.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Privacy First</h2>
    <p>
      All processing happens locally in your browser. We don't store, transmit, or analyze your data. 
      Your privacy is our priority.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Open Source</h2>
    <p>
      DevTools is open source and available on GitHub. Contributions and feedback are welcome!
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>


